---
import Card from './Card.astro';
---

<section class="bg-[#212223] text-[#f5f5f5] py-10 px-6">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <Card title="Full-fledged scripting & expressions" description="Use powerful scripts and expressions to control widgets dynamically." />
    <Card title="User-defined widget trees & composition" description="Build complex interfaces by composing custom widget trees effortlessly." />
    <Card title="Built-in configuration libraries" description="Leverage prebuilt libraries for easy configuration and setup of your widgets." />
    <Card title="Builtin tooling for better developer experience" description="Tools designed to streamline development, debugging, and deployment." />
    <Card title="X11 + Wayland compatibility" description="Seamlessly run your widgets on both X11 and Wayland environments." />
    <Card title="Hot Reload" description="Instantly see changes during development without restarting your app." />
  </div>
</section>
